Label: Sal Box
Comment: Named the "Sal Box" as a Sal I restriction endonuclease site is located within the sequence. An 18 base pair sequence element found in multiple copies in the nontranscribed spacer downstream of the 18S rRNA coding region.  This element provides the termination signal for ribosomal gene transcription.
